properties.otherAdvice:
Special event clearways will be in effect on roads in North Sydney from 2am Saturday 14 November until 2am Monday 16 November to accommodate rail replacement bus operations for Sydney Trains trackwork.

Clearways will be in effect on the eastern side of Miller St from the Pacific Hwy to Blue St and on the western side of Pacific Hwy from Blue St to Miller St.

Clearways are strict no-parking zones and apply even to local residents or RMS Mobility Scheme Permit holders. Check signs before parking as vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.
